@NODE Intro "Welkome Dear Reader..."


                           @{b}A s c i i   T e r r o r@{ub}

                     short info text about this pack...

Ascii Terror is created for your pleasure and it covers new ascii collections
as well as the old ones done by all ascii makers I have ever had on my screen
in my whole fukkin' life.

If  you  have all issues of this pack and @{b}STILL@{ub} have some other ascii collies
please support me.  Why should not these files be shown to public?  God bless
you,  dear  supporters.   Well  if you want to contact me (Paszczak - ascii &
this pack maker) click @{" THIS " LINK "Contact Me"} gadget.

@ENDNODE


;%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
;                           i n f o r m a t i o n s
;%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%

@NODE Informations "Some Infos About The World We Live In..."


                         @{b}W e l k o m e   A g a i n !@{ub}

This is our 10th meeting in my "not so famous" asc2 pack called Ascii Terror.
In  current  issue  I  brought  to  you  with really big pleasure about 2,000
kilobytes  of ascii collections.  Enjoy them and support this pack by sending
collections never included in my pack.  Hope you also enjoyed previous issues
of  pack.   If  not  please @{" CONTACT ME " LINK "Contact Me"} and  tell about your imagination of
future editions.


Many of you may surely ask why I publish such a pack. Here's an explanation:

Ascii  art  grows day by day and there are lotsa collections on elite boards.
Have you leeched ·ALL· of them or only those from famous artists, missing new
talents  as  well  as great collections?  This pack allows you to have almost
(because  it depends on traders of course) all newest productions released on
ascii scene.

By  using  AmigaGuide  system  you  have  an easy access to all those megz of
collies & if you need something (a download logos for example) you search for
your  favourite  artists  and  cut the logos off directly to your board.  The
Ascii  Terror  pack  is also low-quality filter for fuckin lame releases.  Of
coz  beginners  are  tolerated but fuck the lameness!  Ascii scene is not for
you, all you rippers & talentless freaks.


Ok, now about my releases in this issue:

Ops. I haven't finished any new ascii collections for this issue, sorry! :-)
Look for further editions for my prods! SOON!


Ok that's all I had to say... And if you wanna contact me click @{" THIS " LINK "Contact Me"}.


                                Yours...

                                     Paszczak of Azkiness
@ENDNODE




