@NODE "Twilight" "Look! There's another ascii team on our scene!"


                        What the FUCK is Twilight!
                        ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
            Twilight or 'tL!' is a little group that I created
           to release Danish BBS list in and maybe other things
                too. I also hope that the group maybe will
                   grow in the future to become a bigger
                     (not too big!) and greater group.

           The history behind Twilight is short. When Superiors
          was born in late winter 1993. I had in a long time with
             some of my friends talked about starting a group.
        Some names came up, Twilight was one of them, but the name
            we took was, as you all know, Superiors. But as you
              maybe also know, Superiors turned in the wrong
            direction, like: crappy releases - lack of support
         at the support boards (if any!) and many-many more shitty
          things. And as the result of all that Superiors 'died'
              in late September 1995 - Almost two years old.
                   But now in 1996 Twilight is born !!!
                (The exactly date was 16th December 1995!)

                The dream with Twilight is not to create a
             group with world-wide members, a group releasing
            new stuff everyday or maybe even a group with some
              traders uploading 100 megz everyday. No I want
             to create a little group where friendship is one
                      of the most importants things.


                               How to join:
                               ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                    We allready have one board, namely:
                Digital Conspiracy and thats our DkHq. You
             could contact me there or at Electronic Confusion
               or Fatal Justice. You don't have to could do
                    anything special. But if you are a
             ascˇˇ/coder/musician/graphician/sysop/trader dude
                       whatever, then give it a try!


                 Complete memberlist of Twilight follows:
                 ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                         n  ·  i  ·  C  ·  K  ·  o


                             Twilight boards:
                             ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
           Digital Conspiracy  [DkHq]  Node #o1  +45-32-4o5-17


                            And another thing:
                            ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
                  Ascii artists is welcome to create both
               Twilight logos and/or Twilight file_id diz's.
@ENDNODE
